Workday Adaptive Planning Bookmarklets

Bookmarks bar

Instructions for Chrome browser:

Make sure your bookmark bar is showing under the URL bar. If you don't see your Bookmark bar, type CTRL + SHIFT + B.

One Step: Simply hover a link below (eg. "Modeling"): click & hold + drag & drop it into the bookmark bar.

*** OR ***

1) Right-click on a link Below (eg. "Modeling") and select "Copy link address".

2) In your bookmark bar: Right-click and select "Add Page". Give your Bookmark a name (eg. "Modeling") and paste the javascript into URL line. Click Save.

Test it!

First, you must login to Adaptive. You *must* always call these bookmarks from a existing logged-in Adaptive session in order to use them (as they will retrieve your current session ID).

Once logged into an Adaptive session: click on your bookmark and it should take you to the page!

Modeling ---> This link will open your Model Management page (equivalent to MENU > Modeling > Model Management)
Lvls ---> This link will open your Levels page (equivalent to MENU > Modeling > Model Management > Levels)
Lvl Attr ---> This link will open your Level Attributes page (equivalent to MENU > Modeling > Model Management > Level Attributes)
Dims ---> This link will open your Dimensions page (equivalent to MENU > Modeling > Model Management > Dimensions)
M>LAS ---> This link will open your Level Assigned Sheets page (equivalent to MENU > Modeling > Model Management > Level Assigned Sheets)
M>UAS ---> This link will open your User Assigned Sheets page (equivalent to MENU > Modeling > Model Management > User Assigned Sheets)
